==== Notes ==== This is for your lazy asf Aurabots that cant read 1000 lines of text. ============= ^xD02090^x70FF70Special thanks to Darkeoj for putting together these notes^7!
Leveling ^xFFFF77-Act 1- ^7Level 2 ^x7070FF^7Vendor (Self): ^x7070FFStormblast Mine^7 Vendor (Spark): ^x70FF70Pierce Support?^7 (If still able)
Level 4- Post Tidal Island & Breaking Eggs Vendor (Self): ^x7070FFFlame Wall, Orb of Storms^7 Quest Reward: ^x7070FFArcane Surge Support, Frostblink, Frostbomb^7 (Tarkleigh)
Level 8 & 10- Post Brutus Quest Reward: ^x7070FF Added Lightning Damage, ^xE05030Leap Slam ^7 ^xAF6025Consideration: ^7TS will need Added Lightning Damage and You will need a second Added Lightning for OoS link
^xFFFF77-Act 2- ^7Level 16 Quest Reward: ^x7070FFHerald of Thunder^7
Level 18 Vendor (Self): ^x7070FFSummon Skitterbots,^x70FF70 Faster Attacks Support^7 Quest Reward: ^x7070FFConcentrated Effect^7
^xFFFF77-Act 3- ^7Level 24 Vendor (Self): ^x7070FFConductivitiy^7 Quest Reward: ^x7070FFWrath^7
Library for Carry: ^x7070FFLightning Penetration ^7OR ^x70FF70Ice Bite
^xFFFF77-Act 4- ^7^xAF6025Consideration: ^7This is only for the AURA SWAP, otherwise skip until you swap over later.
Vendors: ^x7070FFDiscipline (A3), Stormblast Mine (Siosa), ^xE05030Generosity (A3), Vitality (A1), Smite (A1), ^x70FF70Faster Attacks Support (A2)
^xAF6025Consideration: ^7THIS IS POSSIBLY OUTDATED DUE TO 3.21 CHANGE 1) 4L: you'll want a ^xE050302r^7^x7070FF1b^7^x70FF701g^7, though if you haven't managed to find a 4 link, a ^x7070FF2b^7^xE050301r^7 works, dropping ^x70FF70Faster Attacks^7. 2) A melee weapon, preferably a ^xC8C8C8cutlass^7, which you should be looking for from the act 4 vendor throughout the act. (Cutlass grants accuracy for smite and has 1.55 base attack speed.) 3) sufficient properly colored sockets to socket everything else, though the only other link is between ^xE05030Leap Slam^7 and ^x70FF70Faster Attacks^7.
Drop ^x7070FFSummon Skitterbots^7, throw in ^xE05030Vitality^7 and ^x7070FFDiscipline^7. (If Able with new Aura Changes) Feel free to unbind your detonate mines button, since you'll always be leaving the mines undetonated on the ground for their offensive aura. From here on out, your order of priority for damage buffs skills is ^xE05030Smite^7^xE05030 ^7>^7 ^x70FF70^x7070FFConductivity^7> ^x7070FFStormblast Mines^7
-Act 5 thru 7- ^7Gems you pickup through these acts are ones you skipped from before. ^x70FF70^7Vendors: ^x70FF70Grace, Vaal Haste, ^x7070FFWrath^7
^xFFFF77-Act 8- ^7Vendors: ^xE05030Defiance Banner (A2) Arrogance Support (A6 Lilly) Determination (A3) ^x7070FFClarity (A1)
^xFFFF77-Afterwards- ^7Grab all other gems as needed, filling in missing spaces.
